('2008-04-18', '04:04:00', 990, 'Blue Tit (Cyanistes caeruleus)', 'Pair of blue tits that have been investigating one of the nesting boxes over the past few days may have decided to nest there. They have spent the afternoon chasing off male and female house sparrows that have been coming near the box to feed from a bird feeder and nibble the buds on a pussy willow tree. The bird feeder is about to be moved further away from the nesting box.', 'Alive', '2', -1.601879597, 54.98895986, 'gardener'),
('2008-04-18', '04:04:00', 1850, 'Collared Dove (Streptopelia decaocto)', 'One collared dove landed briefly on the garage roof. First one I&#39;ve seen this year. We usually have a couple visiting regularly.', 'Alive', '2', -1.601879597, 54.98895986, 'gardener'),
('2008-04-18', '08:04:00', 871, 'Blackbird (Turdus merula)', '2 males fighting on garage roof - quite intensive, lasted 4 minutes. Not clear from their behaviour when they left in opposite directions which one had &#39;won&#39;.', 'Alive', '2', -1.601890326, 54.98892908, 'gardener'),
